snippet.title: Unwell Live-Action Trailer
snippet.description:
ADD UNWELL TO YOUR WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2662070/Unwell/

There is something in the deep. Perhaps a key to solving your own life equation.

Updates to the demo version come every Friday.

Unwell presents a story based on the actual works of Dr. Freud and Dr. Hawkins.

Unwell is available for Windows and Linux.

Make sure to:

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100086493574526
Follow us on X: https://x.com/Main_Protege

Special thanks to the City of Głogów, which made these recordings possible!
